        "richTextValue" : "<p><strong style=\"font-size: 22px;\">My Benefits</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">Click the image below to find out more about Blue Arrows Free Flexible Employee Assistance Programme</span></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://impellam.lightning.force.com/sfc/servlet.shepherd/version/renditionDownload?rendition=ORIGINAL_Png&amp;versionId=068Q500000DFrMS&amp;operationContext=CHATTER&amp;contentId=05TQ500000HOFRy\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"sfdcCbImage\" alt=\"\" src=\"{!contentAsset.Blue_Arrow_Flexible_Employee_Assist1.4}\" style=\"width: 255.234px; height: 360.891px;\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://impellam--test.sandbox.my.salesforce.com/sfc/p/3L0000000lMO/a/3L0000001GsQ/K3p5NRQ97aqtUPaHM0KPPXt4XVBRkDrlIGTrhl_G7T0\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><img class=\"sfdcCbImage\" alt=\"\" src=\"{!contentAsset.Blue_Arrow_Flexible_Employee_Assist.1}\"></a></p>\n<p><strong style=\"font-size: 20px;\">My HR Policies &amp; Flexible employee handbook</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">See list below for all available documents, click on a document name to view and download a copy</span></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://impellam.my.salesforce.com/sfc/p/0Y000000LzSj/a/4J0000003KzW/1FdJnvpElF4r6AscHggluOltXQIFgZPoYPq4wEV1IOo\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: arial;\">Blue Arrow - FE Handbook</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://impellam.my.salesforce.com/sfc/p/#0Y000000LzSj/a/4J000000j8Dz/2a9UJr2IfoKXoXCpcJnsonOMmFC4JyHaREUJQTklB8M\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: arial;\">Blue Arrow - FE Public Interest Disclosure (Whistleblowing) Policy</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://impellam.my.salesforce.com/sfc/p/0Y000000LzSj/a/4J000000j8E4/Bf8Gd5FwvOJsCIG7ikx5sIuZWFLrTOzZhjQcnJPQF14\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" 